## Spacing Rhythm

| Context | Value |
|---|---|
| Between hero elements | `gap-6` to `gap-8` |
| Between page sections | `py-24` to `py-32` |
| Card grids | `gap-4` to `gap-6` |
| Text blocks | `space-y-4` |
| Section intro → grid | `mt-16` |

---

## ❌ Anti-Patterns
- `rounded-xl` / `rounded-2xl` → max `rounded-sm`, prefer `rounded-none`
- `shadow-md` / `shadow-lg` → custom rgba drop-shadow or text-shadow only
- Any color outside black / gold / bone palette (no blues, greens, purples)
- White backgrounds anywhere → use `bg-[#0a0a0a]` or `bg-black/80 backdrop-blur`
- `font-bold` on lore body text → EB Garamond weight reads naturally
- Centered body text in long paragraphs → always left-aligned
- Generic loading spinners → use fade transition or pulsing glyph
